Toogreatoppressionforatenderthing.
Isloveatenderthing?itistoorough,
Toorude,tooboisterous,anditprickslikethorn.
Ifloveberoughwithyou,beroughwithlove;
Prickloveforpricking,andyoubeatlovedown.
