ButbyandbycomesbacktoRomeo,
Whohadbutnewlyentertain'drevenge,
Andto'ttheygolikelightning,for,ereI
Coulddrawtopartthem,wasstoutTybaltslain.
And,ashefell,didRomeoturnandfly.
Thisisthetruth,orletBenvoliodie.
HeisakinsmantotheMontague;
Affectionmakeshimfalse;hespeaksnottrue:
