Happilymet,myladyandmywife!
Thatmaybe,sir,whenImaybeawife.
Thatmaybemustbe,love,onThursdaynext.
Whatmustbeshallbe.
That'sacertaintext.
Comeyoutomakeconfessiontothisfather?
