Peace,ho,forshame!confusion'scurelivesnot
Intheseconfusions.Heavenandyourself
Hadpartinthisfairmaid;nowheavenhathall,
Andallthebetterisitforthemaid:
Yourpartinheryoucouldnotkeepfromdeath,
Butheavenkeepshispartineternallife.
Themostyousoughtwasherpromotion;
For'twasyourheavensheshouldbeadvanced:
Andweepyenow,seeingsheisadvanced
Abovetheclouds,ashighasheavenitself?
O,inthislove,youloveyourchildsoill,
Thatyourunmad,seeingthatsheiswell:
She'snotwellmarriedthatlivesmarriedlong;
Butshe'sbestmarriedthatdiesmarriedyoung.
Dryupyourtears,andstickyourrosemary
Onthisfaircorse;and,asthecustomis,
Inallherbestarraybearhertochurch:
Forthoughfondnaturebidsusanlament,
Yetnature'stearsarereason'smerriment.
Allthingsthatweordainedfestival,
Turnfromtheirofficetoblackfuneral;
Ourinstrumentstomelancholybells,
Ourweddingcheertoasadburialfeast,
Oursolemnhymnstosullendirgeschange,
Ourbridalflowersserveforaburiedcorse,
Andallthingschangethemtothecontrary.
