IfImaytrusttheflatteringtruthofsleep,
Mydreamspresagesomejoyfulnewsathand:
Mybosom'slordsitslightlyinhisthrone;
Andallthisdayanunaccustom'dspirit
Liftsmeabovethegroundwithcheerfulthoughts.
Idreamtmyladycameandfoundmedead--
Strangedream,thatgivesadeadmanleave
tothink!--
Andbreathedsuchlifewithkissesinmylips,
ThatIrevived,andwasanemperor.
Ahme!howsweetisloveitselfpossess'd,
Whenbutlove'sshadowsaresorichinjoy!
